n get better terms — whether that''s lower cost of capital, higher advance rates, or longer tenor on the debt.","Cloud providers especially benefit because the utilization model means GPUs cycle through faster — having residual value coverage from day one protects the financing.","I''m not trying to sell anything on this call — I just want to see if it''s worth 20 minutes with my co-founders Isaac and Josh to walk through how it works.","If it helps, we''re not asking you to change your financing structure. We slot into whatever you already have or are building."],"followups":["Do you already have a lender asking about collateral value at maturity for your upcoming deployments?","Are you financing owned GPUs, leased, or both?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.584Z"}', '');
