ugh how it works.","If it helps, we''re not asking you to change your financing structure. We slot into whatever you already have or are building."],"followups":["Do you already have a lender asking about collateral value at maturity for your upcoming deployments?","Are you financing owned GPUs, leased, or both?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.581Z"}', '');
