gned to make your existing credit process work better for hardware-backed lending.","Would it be worth a 20-minute call with our founders to walk through a couple of real deal structures where this has made a difference?"],"followups":["What''s the typical tenor you''re comfortable with on hardware-backed facilities?","Is the bigger constraint on your side advance rate, or residual value assumptions?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.585Z"}', '');
