ene Street, Suite 2150, Greensboro, NC 27401', NULL, '2026-03-25T16:38:05.442Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uncontacted', '0', '336-676-4476', '{"points":["I''ve been looking at Topsail Re (Topsail Holdings, Inc.)''s work — closely-held cayman islands reinsurer founded late 2018 by former jlt re/axiom re executive david johnson. We think there''s an interesting intersection with GPU infrastructure financing.","The GPU financing market is scaling rapidly, and the biggest structural gap is residual value risk — nobody''s been able to price it well until now.","We''re building the solution that sits between operators and lenders to make GPU-backed deals work at scale.","We think there could be an interesting partnership or distribution angle worth exploring — would a 20-minute call make sense?"],"followups":["Is this a space you''re actively exploring, or more something on the horizon?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.579Z"}', '');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO companies (id, name, type, website, description, priority, industry_segment, estimated_gpu_scale, financing_status, qualification_score, created_at, updated_at, founded_year, employee_count, total_raised, last_funding_round, investors, headquarters, linkedin_url, twitter_url, github_url, recent_news, hiring_signals, last_enriched_at, sec_ticker, sec_cik, gpu_asset_value, depreciation_schedule, open_roles_count, key_hires, nvidia_partnership, outreach_status, manual_call_made, phone, talking_points, call_notes) VALUES ('e46b59cb-f419-4c23-8d61-ed6a513ca073', 'Antares Re (Bermuda)', 'arranger', 'https://www.antaresmanage.com', 'Bermuda-based specialty reinsurer, ABIR member. Managed by Antares Managing Agency (Lloyd''s Syndicate 1274). Backed by GIC (Government of Singapore Investment Corp). Writes specialty lines with Lloyd''s integration. Financial lines, professional indemnity, D&O, cyber, property specialty. | Financial lines and specialty reinsurance active. GIC backing means long-term patient capital. Bermuda entity enables direct engagement. GPU RVG could fit in financial/specialty quota share. Medium-term consideration after Priority A/B outreach. | Domicile: bermuda | Go-direct: medium | Specialty: Financial lines, D&O, professional indemnity, cyber, property specialty', 'B', NULL, NULL, NULL, '62', '2026-03-21 21:54:03', '2026-03-25 14:29:22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Hamilton, Bermuda', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-25T16:44:02.451Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uncontacted', '0', '(703) 276-0100', '{"points":["I''ve been looking at Antares Re (Bermuda)''s work — bermuda-based specialty reinsurer, abir member. We think there''s an interesting intersection with GPU infrastructure financing.","The GPU financing market is scaling rapidly, and the biggest structural gap is residual value risk — nobody''s been able to price it well until now.","We''re building the solution that sits between operators and lenders to make GPU-backed deals work at scale.","We think there could be an interesting partnership or distribution angle worth exploring — would a 20-minute call make sense?"],"followups":["Is this a space you''re actively exploring, or more something on the horizon?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.579Z"}', '');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO companies (id, name, type, website, description, priority, industry_segment, estimated_gpu_scale, financing_status, qualification_score, created_at, updated_at, founded_year, employee_count, total_raised, last_funding_round, investors, headquarters, linkedin_url, twitter_url, github_url, recent_news, hiring_signals, last_enriched_at, sec_ticker, sec_cik, gpu_asset_value, depreciation_schedule, open_roles_count, key_hires, nvidia_partnership, outreach_status, manual_call_made, phone, talking_points, call_notes) VALUES ('1eb9678e-771c-4abd-b934-5c4c3f5a1099', 'Northern Reinsurance SPC, Ltd. (Northern Re)', 'arranger', 'https://www.northernreins.com', 'Cayman Islands-domiciled collateralized reinsurer (Class B(iii) SPC), launched Jan 1, 2023. Wholly owned by NoRe Holdings (NYC). Founded by Anthony McKelvy (ex-Willis Re, Guy Carpenter, Boost Insurance) and Peter McKelvy. Capital raised to $75M after initial $25M. Focus: high-frequency, low-severity risks — personal and commercial auto, general liability, workers compensation, professional lines. CIRCA board member (Peter McKelvy). ILS/collateralized structure. | P&C collateralized reinsurer actively writing specialty commercial lines. Professional lines and GL in scope. Insurtech-native founders (Boost Insurance background) means comfort with tech-adjacent risks. Collateralized structure could be adapted for GPU RVG ILS structure. $75M capital = smaller capacity but direct engagement and innovative structure possible. CIRCA membership = easy Cayman direct approach. | Domicile: cayman | Go-direct: high | Specialty: Personal/commercial auto, general liability, workers compensation, professional lines, high-frequency low-severity specialty', 'B', NULL, NULL, NULL, '65', '2026-03-21 21:54:03', '2026-03-25 14:29:22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands (holding company in New York, NY)', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/northern-re', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-25T16:44:02.451Z', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uncontacted', '0', '893-2778739', '{"points":["I''ve been looking at Northern Reinsurance SPC, Ltd. (Northern Re)''s work — cayman islands-domiciled collateralized reinsurer (class b(iii) spc), launched jan 1, 2023. We think there''s an interesting intersection with GPU infrastructure financing.","The GPU financing market is scaling rapidly, and the biggest structural gap is residual value risk — nobody''s been able to price it well until now.","We''re building the solution that sits between operators and lenders to make GPU-backed deals work at scale.","We think there could be an interesting partnership or distribution angle worth exploring — would a 20-minute call make sense?"],"followups":["Is this a space you''re actively exploring, or more something on the horizon?"],"generated_at":"2026-03-25T14:29:22.579Z"}', '');

