t facility found = potential greenfield. German HQ may mean legal complexity."}', '2026-03-21 02:49:33');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO research_notes (id, company_id, source_url, summary, raw_data, created_at) VALUES ('82873310-fd70-4c7c-8e8c-7fbde0f04ebe', '0a01cc52-7454-4a00-9e58-0649d150ef22', 'https://cirrascale.com', 'Good fit — unique multi-vendor GPU infrastructure, active deployment at scale. No identified CFO/finance lead — David Driggers is CEO/CTO combo, likely handles major financial decisions. Acquisition by BOXX means there''s a parent company finance structure to navigate. Residual value coverage conversation may need to go through BOXX.

GPU scale: Multi-GPU dedicated cloud: NVIDIA (HGX H200, HGX B200/Blackwell), AMD, Cerebras, Qualcomm. AI Innovation Cloud. Only GPUaaS partnering with all major chip vendors.

Funding: Acquired by BOXX in May 2017. Funding history unclear ($2M–$57M range cited across sources — likely confusion). No recent public raise.

